description: This spatial coverage includes vector points and point labels that describe CORDIO and PRAREV in-water survey sites of the broader Djibouti Seascape. Each site has a set of fish and benthic community variables distinguishing it from the surrounding sites. These characteristics include site name, functional group, mean fish biomass (kg/ha) and mean fish abundance (individuals/ha).
name: Djibouti 2014  & 2016 Herbivores & Detritivores Abundance #Individuals/ha
